QuestData.Title: Lok-rath is Secured
QuestData.Description: With their leader dead, the remaining Warsong will be easier to finish.$B$BAs soon as that's done, I'll pull our soldiers out of Lok-rath and head for Grommashar.$B$BIf you're heading back to Telaari Station, would you please inform D'kaan?
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Rangari D'kaan at Telaari Station.
QuestData.RewardText: If you hadn't gone to Lok-rath, our forces would have been decimated.$B$BI'm sorry to hear they laid a trap for you. I guess you have a reputation now.
